{"tid":1021372,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【或會參演新作】「哈利仔」丹尼爾力撐《哈利波特》重拍","createTime":"2019-02-14T08:10:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-23T13:25:28.000Z","uid":130626,"like":124,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"f427ae13b2e8b01bb1501dd8e56a71d515fa5428","tid":1021372,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T08:10:23.000Z","msg":"《哈利波特》（Harry Potter）系列男主角，29歲男星丹尼爾拉德克里夫（Daniel Radcliffe）因電影大賣而廣為人識，最近他就於訪問中，大方表示希望電影有機會重拍：「我肯定會有一些不同版本，我知我不是人生中見到的最後一個哈利波特，可以見到這些電影長存，將會很有趣。」更期待見到新一任「哈利仔」出現：「如果電影重頭拍過都將會很有趣，我將會很想看。」<br />\n其實早前他於訪問中，已被問到會否參演新《哈利波特》的其中一角，他就表示：「某程度上，故事的話劇版與《怪獸與牠們的產地》等作品，人們都想見到我參與其中，但現時任何一方面沒有事情發生，這一刻，我仍很享受演其他不同的東西。」但就表示不抗拒回歸這個魔法世界。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190214/large/1550121117_3ff7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190214%2Flarge%2F1550121117_3ff7.jpg&h=467f07f2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"554fb717b49eea65d77b35f28c0992e802ab13eb","tid":1021372,"uid":50658,"like":279,"dislike":32,"score":247,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T08:11:54.000Z","msg":"我淨係想睇emma watson，其他是但"},{"pid":"22b42c188d375a40c5408918b4a1c4dba95c237c","tid":1021372,"uid":196924,"like":286,"dislike":3,"score":283,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T08:12:27.000Z","msg":"做James Potter囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0052bd7242eea8a43f91504ae0fdf40bf67a1ef6","tid":1021372,"uid":28181,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T08:13:27.000Z","msg":"點解哈利波特唔拍劇？"},{"pid":"8f847f48044e2fa5538e11241701f9d6fe2d259d","tid":1021372,"uid":21398,"like":244,"dislike":0,"score":244,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T08:14:57.000Z","msg":"而家個樣做天狼星就得"},{"pid":"682db092e4bea75088d9f4dba3eae19cdc4cd5d0","tid":1021372,"uid":83102,"like":92,"dislike":0,"score":92,"quote":{"pid":"0052bd7242eea8a43f91504ae0fdf40bf67a1ef6","tid":1021372,"uid":28181,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"